  "translated_text": "Hyundai Card's lifestyle brand PRIVIA, which provides one-stop services in travel and shopping, also offers educational services including early study abroad programs and gifted education camps. PRIVIA Education plans to operate overseas English camps in various regions including the United States, Australia, Canada, and the Philippines, as well as gifted camps for science-gifted students during winter vacation.

